## Motion and Interaction System

Motion principle:
- atmospheric, restrained, intentional

Use Framer Motion for:
- fade/slide reveal on section entry
- staggered text in hero (short sequence only)
- subtle hover states on cards/buttons
- optional low-amplitude parallax in hero visual

Do not use:
- bounce animations
- large elastic easings
- motion that delays content readability

Performance rules:
- respect prefers-reduced-motion
- animation duration mostly 180-450ms
- keep simultaneous animated elements low

---

## Accessibility and Quality Gates

Required:
- semantic landmarks: header, main, section, footer
- keyboard navigation for all interactive elements
- visible focus styles (2px min ring or equivalent)
- color contrast WCAG AA
- alt text on all meaningful images
- skip-to-content link

Lighthouse targets:
- Performance: 90+
- Accessibility: 95+
- Best Practices: 90+
- SEO: 90+

Core Web Vitals intent:
- LCP under 2.5s on average modern mobile
- CLS under 0.1
- INP under 200ms target

