## Final QA Checklist (Ship Readiness)

Layout:
- No horizontal overflow at 320px, 375px, 768px, 1024px, 1440px
- Section spacing consistency preserved across breakpoints
- Proof blocks maintain hierarchy on both desktop and mobile

Interaction:
- All CTAs keyboard-accessible and visibly focused
- Hover states never hide essential content
- Reduced-motion mode remains polished

Content:
- Headlines concise and non-generic
- Proof blocks present clear problem, solution, and stack
- Contact paths obvious and immediate

Performance:
- Images optimized and lazy-loaded where below the fold
- No unnecessary client-side heavy bundles in above-the-fold content
- Lighthouse and CWV targets meet baseline

If all checklist items pass, the blueprint is considered actionable, efficient, and clean across Desktop and Mobile.
